                Engineering Career Center
              
College of Engineering 









Employers





      View Menu
      
Down arrow icon












Welcome to Engineering and Computer Science at UIC! The Engineering Career Center is happy to assist you with all of your internship and entry-level recruitment needs.
At UIC, employers can recruit from a variety of engineering and technology majors including: Bioengineering, Chemical Engineering, Civil Engineering, Computer Engineering, Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, Energy Engineering, Industrial Engineering, Engineering Management, and Mechanical Engineering.
Comprised of over 5,000 undergraduate and graduate students, UIC is home to over 30 engineering student organizations, $83 million in research funding, and over 25,000 alumni.
Learn how to engage with our students by visiting our engagement page and contacting us to get started recruiting on campus!





Contact Us!





